issue.title: Feedback2 fixes for problems 1-3
issue.body:
Problem 1 fixed.
Specific cause for problem 2-3 seemed to be missing "unhandled" intent. Seems to not crash for that reason any more after adding to all states.
Problems 4-5 are design issues, so have not been fixed.
